{"tid":1199884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"溫和派可以有大把嘢做，入黎我講你知","createTime":"2019-06-10T15:16:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T15:26:50.000Z","uid":63154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"73312b8bd4af01dd35719dbaa590e053429044e1","tid":1199884,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:16:46.000Z","msg":"大量鏡頭影住每一角落，每一段衝突，黑就用大光燈，唔好再俾暗角事件發生，所有嘢都要影住，即時upload走，因為差佬有可能會埋黎收你機，如果你得offline copy，等於白做<br />\n<br />\n準備BB油幫人沖走胡椒噴霧，有人教過用油唔好用水，係印走唔係抹走<br />\n<br />\n外圍發展要通知內部，有幾多人黎緊，咩裝備，咩方向黎，搵方法通知啲激動人士，可能要人傳人，到時電話可能被jam咗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係諗到咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f5fd1584cad5cbb0e1879c777a8bd171c029c2","tid":1199884,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:25:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/10/232541_509aab227c0e7eee27f2ed358cf41cec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F10%2F232541_509aab227c0e7eee27f2ed358cf41cec.png&h=4cc057ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（文宣組）612icon<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1199744\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1199744</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"35d7bfbdcd16a6706c0c307e66a5831cde12ec6e","tid":1199884,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:26:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}